description: Demo of Azi library This is a Demo of Azi library. Azi is a library for init Termux-like app. On first run, Azi will extract a zip from apk's assets, and then call /system/bin/sh to run azi_init.sh to do some setup. After that, user can edit data files easily in /sdcard/Android/data directory of this app. This app can be used to test how Azi works on a device. This app ONLY support aarch64 (arm64) CPU !!
